author: cmpilato
msg: * subversion/tools/backup/hot-backup.py.in

delete.  This was causing nothing to be removed on svn.collab.net
(because there are dirs named 'svn-1234.KEEP' in the directory).

author: striker
msg: * subversion/libsvn_delta/diff_file.c
(svn_diff__file_datasource_open): Stop reserving an extra byte of memory
and writing a '\n' sentinel in that byte.
(svn_diff__file_datasource_get_next_token):
Use memchr instead of strchr so we don't crash on binary files.  Also
update the eol logic now we are not using a '\n' sentinel.
This is an empty revision for padding.
